I'm ERPB Inspector Im Han-rim.

535
00:39:26.864 --> 00:39:28.824
You fucking bitch!

536
00:39:34.080 --> 00:39:34.914
Let go.

537
00:39:35.539 --> 00:39:37.208
Let go. you fucking…

538
00:39:40.086 --> 00:39:42.338
You punk. You sure talk a lot. don't you?

539
00:39:43.089 --> 00:39:44.924
