547
00:40:49.864 --> 00:40:50.906
So.

548
00:40:51.449 --> 00:40:53.534
any bastard who gets in the way of that…

549
00:41:01.208 --> 00:41:02.543
no matter who they are…

550
00:41:04.420 --> 00:41:07.047
