554
00:41:26.817 --> 00:41:27.860
Please.

555
00:41:28.736 --> 00:41:30.112
Please give me another chance.

556
00:41:31.280 --> 00:41:33.866
Chances aren't something you're given.

557
00:41:35.075 --> 00:41:37.453
They come to those who want them.

558
00:41:41.832 --> 00:41:45.711
<i>I wanted to give you a chance.</i>

559
00:41:47.588 --> 00:41:49.131
<i>But Gyu-cheol.</i>

560
00:41:50.508 --> 00:41:52.009
<i>the thing is.</i>

561
00:41:53.511 --> 00:41:55.054
<i>chances aren't given to you.</i>

562
00:41:58.265 --> 00:42:00.809
Chances only come to those who want them.

563
00:42:05.814 --> 00:42:06.899
<i>Wow.</i>

564
00:42:08.651 --> 00:42:10.694
You really were made for each other.

565
00:42:14.240 --> 00:42:16.825
