567
00:42:21.330 --> 00:42:23.207
you shouldn't do this."

568
00:42:26.961 --> 00:42:29.672
Why the fuck shouldn't I?

569
00:42:30.673 --> 00:42:32.341
Don't bullshit me.

570
00:42:33.300 --> 00:42:35.261
Don't pretend you care.

571
00:42:36.345 --> 00:42:39.056
I don't need a stupid chance.
Just kill me instead.

572
00:42:40.224 --> 00:42:42.518
Go on. Kill me.

573
00:42:43.686 --> 00:42:45.062
I said kill me.

574
00:43:18.220 --> 00:43:20.973
Gyu-cheol. you shouldn't do this.

575
00:43:21.849 --> 00:43:23.100
It's okay.

576
00:43:26.437 --> 00:43:27.938
Let's start over.

577
00:43:46.498 --> 00:43:50.044
This is the last chance
Ms. Choi is giving you.

578
00:44:05.100 --> 00:44:07.645
Fuck!

579
00:44:09.605 --> 00:44:12.149
Who do you think you all are?

580
00:44:12.983 --> 00:44:15.152
You think you're Jesus?

581
00:44:15.235 --> 00:44:17.029
A damn Buddha. or what?

582
00:44:17.112 --> 00:44:20.407
Fuck!

583
00:44:28.040 --> 00:44:29.750
We're adults. you punk. Adults.

584
00:44:48.018 --> 00:44:49.353
I did you proud. right?

585
00:46:03.302 --> 00:46:04.636
Shall I get you a stapler?

586
00:46:08.098 --> 00:46:09.183
Oh man.

587
00:46:10.058 --> 00:46:11.560
Don't make me laugh.

588
00:46:28.577 --> 00:46:29.870
For fuck's sake!

589
00:46:29.953 --> 00:46:31.038
I'm going! Damn it.

590
00:46:32.206 --> 00:46:34.124
-You'll be okay.
-Thank you.

591
00:46:35.918 --> 00:46:38.337
-Let go of me.
-Let go. damn it.

592
00:46:39.004 --> 00:46:40.214
Fucking hell.

593
00:46:40.297 --> 00:46:41.715
I'm going. man!

594
00:46:49.223 --> 00:46:50.307
You

595
00:46:51.016 --> 00:46:52.643
are being charged

596
00:46:53.560 --> 00:46:55.103
with violations of the ERPB Act.

597
00:46:56.230 --> 00:46:57.564
