-Are you okay?

609
00:47:53.579 --> 00:47:55.122
-That bastard!
-Hey. stop him!

610
00:47:56.248 --> 00:47:57.249
Hey. you punk!

611
00:47:57.332 --> 00:47:59.251
-That's my son-in-law. you punk!
-Stop.

612
00:47:59.334 --> 00:48:02.254
Get out here! You punk. come here!

613
00:48:02.337 --> 00:48:04.298
-Come here!
-Go.

614
00:48:04.381 --> 00:48:05.799
-Minister. please.
-Please go!

615
00:48:05.883 --> 00:48:06.800
Come here. bastard!

616
00:48:06.884 --> 00:48:09.344
-Hold on. Minister.
-Come back! Hey!

617
00:48:10.012 --> 00:48:11.513
-Hey!
-Minister. wait.

618
00:48:11.597 --> 00:48:13.557
-Are you okay?
-Are you all right?

619
00:48:13.640 --> 00:48:14.975
MINISTRY OF EDUCATION

620
00:48:15.058 --> 00:48:16.101
<i>Fellow citizens.</i>

621
00:48:16.602 --> 00:48:19.104
do you know the definition of education?

622
00:48:19.938 --> 00:48:23.525
"The teaching of knowledge and skills
and the cultivation of character."

623
00:48:24.026 --> 00:48:26.069
This is what education is.

624
00:48:26.820 --> 00:48:29.865
Yes. good universities and good jobs
are important.

625
00:48:29.948 --> 00:48:31.491
But what's more important

626
00:48:31.575 --> 00:48:35.871
is nurturing a person's dignity
and moral integrity.

627
00:48:35.954 --> 00:48:40.042
This is putting the true meaning
of education into practice.

628
00:48:41.501 --> 00:48:46.256
<i>However. the current education system</i>
<i>of our country has strayed too far</i>

629
00:48:46.340 --> 00:48:48.467
<i>from this purpose and is deeply broken.</i>

630
00:48:49.968 --> 00:48:52.888
<i>Nonetheless. in the midst of this reality.</i>

631
00:48:53.847 --> 00:48:57.768
<i>most teachers in this country</i>
<i>continue to fulfill their calling.</i>

632
00:48:57.851 --> 00:49:01.688
<i>teaching children and trying to guide them</i>
<i>toward the right path.</i>

633
00:49:10.781 --> 00:49:13.450
How long must we continue to see

634
00:49:14.284 --> 00:49:15.494
students and teachers

635
00:49:16.244 --> 00:49:19.289
never making it back home

636
00:49:20.666 --> 00:49:22.334
from school?

637
00:49:24.836 --> 00:49:28.382
The ERPB will uphold
the value of education

638
00:49:29.174 --> 00:49:30.676
and protect victims…

639
00:49:32.594 --> 00:49:35.847
until schools are no longer places
of fear and anxiety

640
00:49:36.598 --> 00:49:38.266
and become truly safe.

641
00:49:38.350 --> 00:49:41.728
We will continue to exist
until our education system is restored…

642
00:49:44.106 --> 00:49:45.524
to its intended state.

643
00:49:56.535 --> 00:50:01.289
I MISS YOUR SMILE SO MUCH

644
