656
00:50:46.877 --> 00:50:48.003
You cried for a month.

657
00:50:48.086 --> 00:50:49.337
-No. that's…
-Oh.

658
00:50:50.047 --> 00:50:51.715
That's actually kind of cute.

659
00:50:51.798 --> 00:50:53.759
He's very cute. He's also very loving.

660
00:50:53.842 --> 00:50:56.011
-And very tearful.
-You're adorable. sir.

661
00:50:56.094 --> 00:50:57.304
Seriously. you punks.

662
00:50:57.387 --> 00:51:01.016
Hey. did you…
finish the report on Jinwon High?

663
00:51:01.099 --> 00:51:02.434
-Come on.
-Send it over now.

664
00:51:02.517 --> 00:51:04.061
