667
00:51:06.646 --> 00:51:09.066
Bullying. my ass.
If you don't want to work. say so.

668
00:51:09.149 --> 00:51:11.401
Got a problem?
We'll settle it under Yatcha rules.

669
00:51:11.485 --> 00:51:13.153
