698
00:52:14.339 --> 00:52:15.173
I see.

699
00:52:16.967 --> 00:52:18.301
<i>Do something.</i>

700
00:52:18.802 --> 00:52:20.345
-What do I do?
-Help me sober up.

701
00:52:20.428 --> 00:52:22.347
-What should I do?
-Just do anything.

702
00:52:22.430 --> 00:52:23.390
Do something.

703
00:52:23.473 --> 00:52:24.933
-Do anything.
-What should I do?

704
00:52:25.016 --> 00:52:26.351
I'm sorry.

705
00:52:37.070 --> 00:52:37.988
Why hold my hand?

706
00:52:38.613 --> 00:52:41.158
-I let you hold my hand. and you…
-You "let" me?

707
00:52:43.160 --> 00:52:45.579
