724
00:53:34.961 --> 00:53:38.298
You should make up for the money
I missed out on by not going pro.

725
00:53:41.843 --> 00:53:42.844
Whatever.

726
00:53:43.428 --> 00:53:44.930
You fucking assholes.

727
