Hey.

729
00:54:06.243 --> 00:54:07.619
You high school punks.

730
00:54:07.702 --> 00:54:10.413
You should be studying. you brats.

731
00:54:10.997 --> 00:54:13.250
Guys. get up.

732
00:54:13.917 --> 00:54:15.126
I said get up.

733
00:54:15.210 --> 00:54:16.544
It's okay. Get up.

734
00:54:17.045 --> 00:54:18.129
Come on. get up.

735
00:54:19.005 --> 00:54:22.008
I'm Deputy Director Bong Geun-dae
from the ERPB.

736
00:54:22.092 --> 00:54:23.385
From this moment on.

737
00:54:24.261 --> 00:54:25.720
the ERPB

738
00:54:27.305 --> 00:54:28.598
will teach you a lesson.

739
00:54:31.309 --> 00:54:32.143
Get up.

740
00:54:32.852 --> 00:54:33.728
I said get up.

741
00:54:33.812 --> 00:54:35.397
You too. Step back.

742
00:54:36.606 --> 00:54:37.732
Get up.

743
00:54:37.816 --> 00:54:39.276
I said get up.

744
00:54:45.615 --> 00:54:46.491
Yes?

745
00:54:50.412 --> 00:54:52.038
-You told me to get up.
