746
00:54:52.122 --> 00:54:53.873
No. I said "get off" me.

747
00:54:53.957 --> 00:54:55.125
You said to get up.

748
00:54:55.208 --> 00:54:57.210
-No. I said. "Get off."
-Oh man.

749
00:54:57.294 --> 00:54:59.296
-You said to get up.
-No. I said. "Get off."

750
00:54:59.379 --> 00:55:02.299
-I said…
-Take your hands off him. Now!

751
00:55:02.966 --> 00:55:03.800
Who's that?

752
00:55:05.552 --> 00:55:06.636
Get up.

753
00:55:08.138 --> 00:55:09.306
Get up!

754
00:55:10.765 --> 00:55:13.184
If they listen to words.
you teach with words.

755
00:55:13.268 --> 00:55:17.188
