777
00:57:04.671 --> 00:57:05.880
Mr. Hwang!

778
00:57:05.964 --> 00:57:07.590
Oh dear.

779
00:57:07.674 --> 00:57:09.092
-Let's get you up.
-Are you okay?

780
00:57:11.678 --> 00:57:12.679
Mark my words.

781
00:57:13.179 --> 00:57:16.516
I'll be back no matter what.
The first thing I'll do is take you down.

782
00:57:21.438 --> 00:57:23.940
When Cho Gyu-cheol gave you the recording.

783
00:57:24.899 --> 00:57:26.025
you knew what happened.

784
00:57:26.985 --> 00:57:28.778
You should've stopped then.

785
00:57:29.571 --> 00:57:33.616
It's adults like you
who turn young students into monsters.

786
00:57:34.117 --> 00:57:37.120
If you can't be a good adult.
at least don't be a bad one.

787
00:57:38.121 --> 00:57:40.707
And what about you? Are you a good adult?

788
00:57:40.790 --> 00:57:43.710
You think I won't find anything on you?
Damn…

789
00:57:57.599 --> 00:57:58.433
I guess

790
00:58:00.018 --> 00:58:03.188
I'm not a good adult either.

791
00:59:28.773 --> 00:59:31.734
Subtitle translation by: Lisa Kim

